          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "...and go back to where they started...",
                "italic": true
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Protagonist returns to their normal world with whatever they found / took – along with a new perspective leading to new wants and needs. This passage back into the normal world mirrors their passage into the unfamiliar world in the Go step. It is a return to familiarity with a new perspective and new abilities."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
