                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Indicate how the Protagonist interacts with the normal world has changed throughout the story."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Example: Feeling they must resort to violence, the Protagonist and their allies return to the village newly armed and with a plan to take the village back and disperse the loggers. "
