          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "...pay its price...",
                "italic": true
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Protagonist Takes what they wanted but pay a steep price, creating a new need that pushes them to the brink. The Protagonist is at their lowest, and all seems lost, leading to the Climax where the Protagonist faces their toughest conflict. This is often where the Protagonist's wants and needs collide."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Demonstrate how the Protagonist actions have serious consequences (e.g. putting more lives at risk, triggering a chase, or causing the Villain to speed up the timeline of their evil plans)."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show the tension and stakes rising as the Protagonist deals with new challenges in the wake of a seeming victory."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Have the Protagonist suffer a significant loss to continue the descent to their lowest (e.g. perhaps a key Ally is killed, an essential item is lost, or they lose the support of an Ally or love interest)."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Example: With their machines destroyed, the loggers turn to violence and attack the village, killing some and holding the rest hostage, intent on ridding themselves of the disruption."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "This step occurs around the 60 - 62% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
